Title: Gwinnett student challenges suspension over ‘Zoom bombing’ allegations
Description: Malachi Battle's lawyers say Gwinnett County schools made the accusation based on faulty computer logs provided by Zoom. a problem that could repeat elsewhere since the company’s online sessions are replacing classrooms for millions of students amid the coronavirus pandemic.
